          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1616425348716-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped broccoli </strong>to the bowl with the breadcrumb mixture and give everything a good mix up until fully combined</p><p>Shape into 3 <strong>patties</strong> per person – these are your <strong>broccoli tots</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>broccoli tots </strong>to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray</p><p>Place the tray[s] under the grill for 10 min or until cooked through and crispy</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? You may need to do this in 2 batches!</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1616425391797-x200.jpg",
