            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>soft cheese</strong>, <strong>chopped sun-dried tomatoes</strong> and 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up then set aside to infuse – this is your <strong>creamy tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1616425470962-x200.jpg",
